995b2fa9-046f-4f1a-9cde-962f4f0bfa64.name: Primary or secondary major declarations
995b2fa9-046f-4f1a-9cde-962f4f0bfa64.description: Students can declare their primary major or second major through a form that can be embedded to and started from the University’s website. After the form is submitted, the academic advisor receives a notification to review the request. If the request is approved, the Registrar is informed to update the Student Information System accordingly.
